She tricked us, right? Gosh.

1765
01:51:09,466 --> 01:51:11,100
(I totally fell for it.)

1766
01:51:11,100 --> 01:51:13,400
(He got tricked.)

1767
01:51:13,400 --> 01:51:14,700
That scared me.

1768
01:51:17,200 --> 01:51:18,100
