1769
01:51:20,633 --> 01:51:22,733
My heart just sank.

1770
01:51:22,733 --> 01:51:24,933
I was ready to step forward and wave.

1771
01:51:28,033 --> 01:51:30,033
Whether I win or not,

1772
01:51:30,600 --> 01:51:31,800
I've been so happy.

1773
01:51:31,800 --> 01:51:33,533
I mean it. Thank you.

1774
01:51:38,833 --> 01:51:41,433
Only one of them...

1775
01:51:41,433 --> 01:51:44,900
will be the winner of Bake Your Dream.

1776
01:51:48,666 --> 01:51:50,900
(The winner will be announced.)

1777
01:51:52,066 --> 01:51:53,933
Is it Hwang Ji Oh?

1778
01:51:55,066 --> 01:51:57,133
Or Kim Si Yeop?

1779
01:51:58,800 --> 01:51:59,966
I'm nervous.

1780
01:52:02,600 --> 01:52:05,633
Who will win...

1781
01:52:06,633 --> 01:52:08,133
the finals?

1782
01:52:09,433 --> 01:52:10,500
Who is it?

1783
01:52:13,633 --> 01:52:16,000
The winner is...

1784
01:52:22,700 --> 01:52:23,866
The glorious winner is...

1785
01:52:29,900 --> 01:52:31,466
I've made it this far.

1786
01:52:31,466 --> 01:52:32,466
I have to win.

1787
01:52:35,333 --> 01:52:36,333
I should turn it around.

1788
01:52:37,333 --> 01:52:38,966
I'll take back the throne.

1789
01:52:42,300 --> 01:52:43,633
The winner is...

1790
01:52:46,433 --> 01:52:47,266
Who is it?

1791
01:52:47,833 --> 01:52:48,633
Let's see.

1792
01:52:51,100 --> 01:52:52,000
Congratulations,

1793
01:52:58,266 --> 01:52:59,466
The winner is...

1794
01:53:02,100 --> 01:53:05,166
Crazy Patissiere, Hwang Ji Oh.

1795
01:53:05,166 --> 01:53:06,166
Congratulations.

1796
01:53:07,366 --> 01:53:10,300
Crazy Patissiere, Hwang Ji Oh.

1797
01:53:10,300 --> 01:53:11,300
Congratulations.

1798
01:53:11,300 --> 01:53:12,600
(We have our glorious winner.)

1799
01:53:12,600 --> 01:53:16,666
(The winner of Bake Your Dream,
Hwang Ji Oh)

1800
01:53:17,975 --> 01:53:20,941
She earned 532 points
in the 1st round of the finals...

1801
01:53:20,966 --> 01:53:23,933
and 765 points in the second round.

1802
01:53:24,700 --> 01:53:28,166
- Her total is 1297 points.
- Good for her.

1803
01:53:28,566 --> 01:53:30,800
Crazy Patissiere, Hwang Ji Oh wins.

1804
01:53:30,800 --> 01:53:33,666
- Congratulations.
- Congratulations.

1805
01:53:34,233 --> 01:53:36,233
She totally dominated Round 2.

1806
01:53:36,233 --> 01:53:38,833
(Ji Oh came back strong
in Round 2 of the finals.)

1807
01:53:40,466 --> 01:53:44,733
- Congratulations.
- Congratulations.

1808
01:53:47,100 --> 01:53:48,933
(Kim Si Yeop, 2nd place, 1262 points)

1809
01:53:48,933 --> 01:53:50,033
I won second place!

1810
01:53:57,633 --> 01:53:59,933
(Patting each other on the back
after a fierce competition)

1811
01:53:59,933 --> 01:54:01,300
- Congratulations.
- Thank you so much.

1812
01:54:01,766 --> 01:54:03,300
- Second place is amazing too.
- Of course.

1813
01:54:04,366 --> 01:54:07,333
Crazy Patissiere, Hwang Ji Oh...

1814
01:54:07,333 --> 01:54:08,800
- Thank you.
- will receive 100,000 dollars...

1815
01:54:08,800 --> 01:54:10,333
and get the opportunity
to launch her own brand.

1816
01:54:10,333 --> 01:54:14,766
She'll also receive a luxury electric SUV.

1817
01:54:16,566 --> 01:54:17,733
Thank you.

1818
01:54:17,733 --> 01:54:23,300
(We have our first winner
of Bake Your Dream.)

1819
01:54:26,500 --> 01:54:29,500
During the competition,

1820
01:54:30,233 --> 01:54:35,900
I realized how lucky I am to have
such amazing people around me.

1821
01:54:37,033 --> 01:54:40,966
I'd like to thank my family
and my grandma as well.

1822
01:54:41,900 --> 01:54:43,000
Most of all...

1823
01:54:52,400 --> 01:54:56,166
This path has a lot of tough moments.

1824
01:54:56,166 --> 01:54:59,900
I got into baking because I wanted to,

1825
01:54:59,900 --> 01:55:01,433
but it can get really tough...

1826
01:55:01,433 --> 01:55:03,166
and overwhelming.

1827
01:55:03,166 --> 01:55:06,400
Sometimes I feel like
I'm not making any progress.

1828
01:55:08,266 --> 01:55:09,586
Whenever I felt that way,

1829
01:55:10,437 --> 01:55:13,133
there was someone
who was like a guiding light for me.

1830
01:55:16,366 --> 01:55:17,200
Who is it?

1831
01:55:19,866 --> 01:55:22,533
It's Pastry Chef Kim Na Rae
who is sitting in the front.

1832
01:55:22,533 --> 01:55:24,433
I met her once when I was in school.

1833
01:55:24,433 --> 01:55:25,400
That's touching.

1834
01:55:27,033 --> 01:55:29,433
I thought I wanted to be like her.

1835
01:55:31,966 --> 01:55:34,500
I watched how she moved forward,

1836
01:55:35,233 --> 01:55:38,433
kept pushing myself,

1837
01:55:38,433 --> 01:55:41,366
and kept working hard to grow.

1838
01:55:50,900 --> 01:55:53,000
I really wanted to win because,

1839
01:55:55,766 --> 01:55:58,266
just like my guiding light, Master Na Rae,

1840
01:56:00,833 --> 01:56:05,466
I want to be a source of hope for someone.

1841
01:56:05,733 --> 01:56:11,600
I'll continue working hard
to become an even better pastry chef.

1842
01:56:11,600 --> 01:56:12,566
Thank you.

1843
01:56:14,266 --> 01:56:15,566
Congratulations.

1844
01:56:15,566 --> 01:56:17,400
Sincere congratulations.

1845
01:56:20,300 --> 01:56:24,500
I saw how hard Ji Oh worked
while competing against her.

1846
01:56:24,500 --> 01:56:26,566
She truly deserves to win.

1847
01:56:27,300 --> 01:56:29,700
It was such a fun experience for me.

1848
01:56:29,700 --> 01:56:31,666
I've been so happy. Thank you!

1849
01:56:36,833 --> 01:56:39,966
Your dreams will continue from here on.

1850
01:56:39,966 --> 01:56:42,266
- Bake your dream!
- Bake your dream!

1851
01:56:46,933 --> 01:56:47,933
Great work.

1852
01:56:49,466 --> 01:56:50,500
Thank you.

1853
01:56:53,300 --> 01:56:55,333
Thanks for your hard work.

1854
01:56:55,333 --> 01:56:56,666
It was really delicious.

1855
01:56:59,600 --> 01:57:00,466
Good work.

1856
01:57:12,900 --> 01:57:20,166
(A journey of over 300 days)

1857
01:57:26,300 --> 01:57:28,633
I've been baking for about 25 years...

1858
01:57:28,633 --> 01:57:30,400
and running my business for 20 years.

1859
01:57:30,700 --> 01:57:33,600
I started baking at 20.

1860
01:57:33,600 --> 01:57:36,266
I'm turning 50 soon.

1861
01:57:36,566 --> 01:57:39,100
I have 45 years of experience.

1862
01:57:39,400 --> 01:57:41,166
I started baking at 15.

1863
01:57:42,600 --> 01:57:44,800
My parents passed away when I was little,

1864
01:57:44,800 --> 01:57:46,666
so I didn't even finish elementary school.

1865
01:57:46,933 --> 01:57:49,933
I just came to Seoul and started baking.

1866
01:57:52,633 --> 01:57:56,566
When I was in 12th grade,
my best friend suddenly suggested...

1867
01:57:56,566 --> 01:57:58,200
we take a baking class together.

1868
01:57:58,200 --> 01:58:00,433
She invited me to learn to bake with her.

1869
01:58:00,966 --> 01:58:03,733
One of the dreams I had was to be a baker.

1870
01:58:03,733 --> 01:58:05,866
I simply thought, "If I became a baker,"

1871
01:58:05,866 --> 01:58:07,700
"I could eat bread every day."

1872
01:58:09,766 --> 01:58:12,700
I loved fresh cream cakes as a kid.

1873
01:58:13,100 --> 01:58:15,254
I started baking
just because I liked cakes,

1874
01:58:15,966 --> 01:58:17,500
and then I really got into it.

1875
01:58:21,033 --> 01:58:24,500
We each stay in our own kitchens...

1876
01:58:24,500 --> 01:58:26,966
and make the same bread.

1877
01:58:28,500 --> 01:58:31,533
I'd been doing the same thing
for 13 years...

1878
01:58:31,533 --> 01:58:34,166
and fell into a slump.

1879
01:58:35,666 --> 01:58:40,166
At one point,
I was baking bread just to make money.

1880
01:58:42,400 --> 01:58:45,533
Then, after joining this competition,

1881
01:58:46,133 --> 01:58:48,433
I realized I truly love baking.

1882
01:58:52,800 --> 01:58:56,500
Even now, baking makes me so happy.

1883
01:58:58,233 --> 01:59:02,233
Nothing makes me prouder
than seeing the finished bread.

1884
01:59:02,900 --> 01:59:04,733
"Your bread is always the best."

1885
01:59:05,600 --> 01:59:08,766
Hearing that just melts away my fatigue.

1886
01:59:08,766 --> 01:59:13,500
It makes me want to keep baking
day after day.

1887
01:59:13,500 --> 01:59:17,433
When I see people enjoy my bread,

1888
01:59:17,766 --> 01:59:20,433
it gives me the confidence...

1889
01:59:20,433 --> 01:59:23,833
that I can bring happiness and joy
to others.

1890
01:59:24,633 --> 01:59:27,366
People can be cold,

1891
01:59:27,366 --> 01:59:29,100
and life can be tough.

1892
01:59:29,100 --> 01:59:32,266
How many jobs are there in the world...

1893
01:59:32,266 --> 01:59:34,666
where you can directly bring happiness
to people...

1894
01:59:34,666 --> 01:59:36,633
like a pastry chef or baker?

1895
01:59:38,066 --> 01:59:41,266
I'll keep challenging myself.

1896
01:59:42,133 --> 01:59:44,533
I won't stop and keep going.

1897
01:59:44,533 --> 01:59:48,400
I'll keep pushing myself
as long as I'm a baker.

1898
01:59:50,566 --> 01:59:55,000
I'll keep putting my all into it.

1899
01:59:56,233 --> 01:59:57,933
My goal after that is...

1900
01:59:58,506 --> 02:00:02,666
to always be there for people...

1901
02:00:04,534 --> 02:00:06,802
in a small bakery.

1902
02:00:08,871 --> 02:00:11,007
I think I might name the bakery
"Bake Your Dream."

1903
02:00:11,007 --> 02:00:13,509
(The Bake Your Dream bonus clip
will be revealed shortly.)

1904
02:00:17,980 --> 02:00:21,217
(Ji Oh has arrived to receive
her winner's prize.)

1905
02:00:32,495 --> 02:00:34,130
Would you open the car for us?

1906
02:00:35,698 --> 02:00:37,333
It's pretty solid, right?

1907
02:00:42,271 --> 02:00:45,708
If you look up, the glass roof...

1908
02:00:45,708 --> 02:00:49,045
gives it a very open feel
with its full panoramic view.

1909
02:00:49,946 --> 02:00:52,114
It also has a power tailgate.

1910
02:00:52,114 --> 02:00:54,283
- The space is quite roomy, right?
- Yes.

1911
02:00:54,850 --> 02:00:58,754
I think one advantage is
how much usable space it has.

1912
02:00:59,288 --> 02:01:02,625
I grew through Bake Your Dream,

1913
02:01:03,259 --> 02:01:07,330
and I think it may have been
the most valuable experience of my life.

1914
02:01:08,431 --> 02:01:10,328
(Kim Jin Seo will also receive
one year of free support.)
